    "created_at": "2023-08-29T08:26:30Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-08-29T08:26:30Z",
    "body": "I think this is an expected behavior to allow more readability.\r\n\r\nThis change will probably don't occur because it would break configuration of all others users.\r\nPlus, starship allow you to simply modify its behavior via a configuration file.\r\n\r\nYou can't ask an application to change the _default_ configuration of **all** existing users just to conform to **your** personal preferences.\r\nIf everyone opens an issue to change the default configuration to suit their preferences, the issue manager will be a mess in no time.\r\n",
