    "created_at": "2023-09-04T17:21:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-09-04T17:21:57Z",
    "body": "I'm not sure what \"as other shells\" means. [Our parent prompt](https://spaceship-prompt.sh/) has this same default behavior, as do the steeef and paradox prompts in [zprezto](https://github.com/sorin-ionescu/prezto). Not everyone likes this, but that's exactly why the configuration file exists in the first place---so that you can change around the prompt to something you like better.\r\n\r\nI need much better evidence than what's presented here in order to entertain a change like this which will affect all users to a significant degree.\r\n\r\n",
